plot: In the latest episode of "IMDb: What to Watch", Keith Simanton talks with actors Seth Rogen, Rose Byrne, Zac Efron, Dave Franco, Christopher Mintz-Plasse, Jerrod Carmichael and director Nicholas Stoller about their movie Neighbors.
